text: DCRI and @verilylifesci will conduct a study to gain insights about the #COVID19 #vaccine developed by @pfizer and BioNTech. The study will follow vaccinated healthcare workers from @HeroesResearch for 2 yrs to collect real-world safety data. More: https://t.co/GvXDwEOgdT https://t.co/X0EnJcVEFo
